[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到誰讓他煉器的！第一章，成績公布。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "上一集，周墨的飛劍搶了考官的儲物袋。這一集，考官終於要公布成績了。周墨到底是被認可，還是被趕出去？答案可能出乎意料。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨，你知不知道你剛才做了什麼？你的飛劍搶了我的儲物袋！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "技術上來說，是飛劍自己決定的。我只是寫了演算法而已。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你還敢狡辯！你知道那裡面有多少靈石嗎？那是我三個月的薪水！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這恰好證明了飛劍的目標鎖定功能非常精準。這是一個亮點。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "亮點？！你管搶劫叫亮點？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "請冷靜。我願意用我剩下的材料來賠償。我還有一個自動按摩陣法和一個智能鬧鐘。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "......誰要你的智能鬧鐘啊。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我宣布，你的入宗考試——"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等一下。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長、長老？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "讓我看看這個年輕人的作品。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這把飛劍......三個微型隱藏機關、指紋識別陣法、自動格式化模組......"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你是說，這把劍會自己找目標、自己鎖定、還有防盜系統？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "是的！我追求的是使用者體驗和底層邏輯閉環。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "有意思......非常有意思。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨，你為什麼要給飛劍裝自動格式化？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "因為萬一飛劍被別人搶走，它會在三分鐘後自動清除所有資料。就像手機一樣。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "......手機是什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "呃，一種......通訊法器。概念上的。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你的腦袋裡裝的都是什麼亂七八糟的。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長老，這個人根本不適合修道！他的煉器方式簡直是褻瀆！"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你說得對。他的方式確實......不合常規。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "對吧！"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "但是，這恰恰是我們煉器峰最需要的。"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三百年来，我們煉器峰的法寶設計越來越保守。大家都只知道照著古方煉，沒有人敢創新。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這個年輕人雖然方法奇怪，但他的思路......是我見過最新穎的。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨，恭喜你。你通過了入宗考試。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "真的嗎？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長老，您不是在開玩笑吧？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "考官，你是不是還想讓他把飛劍收回來？"
      },
      {
        "character": "examiner",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "......他還沒收回去嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "對，我說了，忘加停止按鈕了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你看，這就說明他的防盜系統做得很好。連他自己都收不回來。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "04-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "感謝收看誰讓他煉器的！第一章第二集，成績公布。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨以他獨特的煉器理念，獲得了煉器峰長老的認可。但考官的儲物袋......至今還沒拿回來。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "下集預告：周墨正式加入煉器峰，他的第一個任務居然是——修丹爐。而且這個丹爐，會說話。"
      }
    ]
  }
